channel.title: Help Me Find This Font, Please
channel.description:
Ok, well, I made this image awhile back on my grandpa's computer, and eversince I've been desperately trying to find the font that I used for it. I think it started with a B, but I'm not sure, so if anyone could please just take 2 minutes to look through their fonts and see if they could match this, it would be greatly appreciated.
[img]http://img479.imageshack.us/img479/8048/revolutionxfe9.png[/img]
